              <figcaption class="image-gallery__slide-caption text-gray-700 text-center text-sm pt-8 md:pt-10">Large groups of people line up to purchase difficult to find items, such as sugar, cooking oil, milk, rice, toilet paper, and baby diapers at price-controlled&nbsp; prices during a government event in Caracas, January 24, 2015.&nbsp;
