<div id="ftn41">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref41" id="_ftn41" name="_ftn41" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><span>[41]</span></span></a> Human Rights Watch interview with Noel Varela, Valencia, June 21, 2016. A doctor at the hospital where Human Rights Watch interviewed Varela confirmed his diagnosis and treatment.</p>
