s-la-salud-aragua/">http://www.elcorreodelor inoco.com/corposalud-aragua-terrorismo-trabajadores-la-salud-aragua/</a> (accessed September 3, 2016); “Twelve nurses were fired after denouncing hospital conditions” (Despidieron a 12 enfermeras por denunciar condiciones hospitalarias), <i>Venezuela Awareness</i>, August 25, 2016, <a href="http://www.venezuelaawareness.com/2016/08/despidieron-a-12-enfermeras-por-denunciar-condiciones-hospitalarias/"><span>http://www.venezuelaawareness.com/2016/08/despidieron-a-12-enfermeras-por-denunciar-condiciones-hospitalarias/</span></a> (accessed September 3, 2016).</p>
